a (GDN/EPGD), Göteborg Landvetter (GOT/ESGG), Kaunas (KUN/EYKA), Almaty (ALA/UAAA), Billund (BLL/EKBI), Warsaw Chopin (WAW/EPWA), Malmö Sturup (MMX/ESMS), Copenhagen Kastrup (CPH/EKCH) and 2 others.",
